Could someone who knows Photonvision look at this and see if it is remotely close to being usable? The docs are rather unclear about implementing 3D AprilTags and knowing which pipeline you are using (the type, not the number, I can see that). None of this has been implemented yet so I am just asking conceptually.

Vision Subsystem
Generic AprilTag Guided Scoring
Automatic Intake
